## 🏢 Triple-Bar Layout System (V5.2.7)
I have refactored the transaction header from a monolithic block into three distinct, high-efficiency bars:
1.  **Main Header**: Brand logo, Bank breadcrumbs, and Unified Upload zone.
2.  **Action Bar**: Dynamic Ref# input, real-time Metrics (Tx count, Total Balance), Search, and Popout tools.
3.  **Switcher Bar**: Account pills now inhabit their own snug row, ensuring 1:1 width alignment with the grid.

> [!TIP]
> **Real Estate Optimization**: Stage side padding was reduced by 10% (32px → 29px), and card heights were compressed to ensure maximum transaction visibility.

## ⚡ Stability & Layout Restoration (V5.2.8)
I have resolved the critical `TypeError` and perfected the 1060px vertical stack for all header bars.

