## 🎨 Aesthetic Polish & Functional Breadcrumbs (V5.2.17)
I have refined the UI for a "slicker" professional look and implemented full-width functional navigation.

### 🛠️ Aesthetic Improvements:
- **Slicker Typography**: Reduced global font sizes (cells and headers) to **11.5px - 12px** for a crisper SaaS density.
- **Compact Header**: Scaled down the Header Card padding and title font to "fit to content".
- **Grid Optimization**: Data columns (Ref, Date, Debit, etc.) now use fixed/snug widths, allowing the **Payee / Description** column to expand and absorb all remaining space.

### 🧭 Navigation & Layout:
- **Functional Breadcrumbs**: "Home" and "Transactions" in the top bar are now active links wired to the app's routing.
- **Full-Width Breadcrumb Bar**: The top breadcrumb bar now stretches wall-to-wall, matching the official V5 design pattern.

## 💎 Glassmorphism Island Stack (V5.2.18)
I have implemented the **"Digital Prism"** glassmorphism aesthetic across the entire island stack (Header Card, Action Bar, and Switcher Bar).

### 🛠️ Key Improvements:
- **Depth & Fidelity**: Applied a `8px` backdrop blur (`backdrop-filter`) and a semi-transparent white background for a premium glass feel.
- **Glossy Highlight**: Added a `1px` glossy top highlight (inset shadow) to create a sharp "Digital Prism" edge.
- **Unified Identity**: Created a shared CSS class `.v5-glass` ensuring all components in the stack share identical translucent properties.

